summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground distribution easements over portions of Hillman's Garden Tracts; Brooklyn Addition; Westwood by the Sound; Section II, Township 25 North, Range 4 East; northeast quarter of Section 30, Township 26 North, Range 4 East; southwest quarter of Section 17, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; and vacated South Hinds Street adjoining Canal Waterway.
